import pytest
from pandasaurus.query import Query

def test_case_1():
    # Cell types: B cell (CL:0000236), T cell (CL:0000084)
    # Slim: blood_and_immune_upper_slim
    print("\nRunning Test Case 1: blood_and_immune_upper_slim")
    q = Query(seed_list=["CL:0000236", "CL:0000084"])
    df = q.minimal_slim_enrichment(slim_list=["blood_and_immune_upper_slim"])
    print(df.head())
    assert not df.empty
    assert "s_label" in df.columns
    assert "o_label" in df.columns

def test_case_2():
    # Cell types: kidney cortical cell (CL:0002681), kidney epithelial cell (CL:0002518)
    # Context: kidney (UBERON:0002113)
    print("\nRunning Test Case 2: Contextual enrichment with kidney")
    q = Query(seed_list=["CL:0002681", "CL:0002518"])
    # "part_of kidney" -> kidney is UBERON:0002113
    df = q.contextual_slim_enrichment(context=["UBERON:0002113"])
    print(df.head())
    assert not df.empty
    assert "s_label" in df.columns
    assert "o_label" in df.columns

if __name__ == "__main__":
    test_case_1()
    test_case_2()
